C R  U  D ( delling with data )

## how many tupes of sql or other words characters in the SQL 

1. DDL ( Data Definition Language )

2. DML ( Data Manipulate Language )
3. DCL ( Data Control Language )
4. TCL ( Transaction Control Language )

5. DQL ( Data Query Language )


1. DDL ( Data Definition Language )

- CREATE ( create database structure ,table structure  or news recods or information inserted)

- ALTER ( Modifies database or table structure ) rename columns , changes the data types remove columns created new columns 

- Rename ( Rename )
Columns -> name -> ->user_info

- TRUNCATE ( Only remove all information at time ) -> Very dengeries 

